2. The 27th day of September 2023 is appointed as the day on which the 
Competition (Amendment) Act 2022 (No. 12 of 2022), other than section 26, 
shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

13 September, 2023. 

SIMON COVENEY, 

Minister for Enterprise, Trade and Employment. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 15th September, 2023.
